     A** AB#PPA1 **************************************************
     A*  FIRM ORDER (EXTENDED)
     A*  J.WATANABE    2017.05.22
     A*************************************************************
     A          R AB#PPA11                  TEXT('ORDER (EXTEND)')
     A            BASKJY         1A         COLHDG('DLT CODE D')
     A            BASKYY         4S 0       COLHDG('DLT YEAR')
     A            BASKMM         2S 0       COLHDG('DLT MONTH')
